window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Years ago, Lindon left his home as a powerless Unsouled. Now, he goes to war with the most powerful beings in the world over the future of Cradle itself.</p> <p>The Weeping Dragon has a grudge to settle, and Lindon intends to take out the Dreadgod with his friends by his side. But rival Monarchs know his plans, and they wonâ€™t let things end so easily.</p> <p>If Lindon does win, he will ascend to the heavens. But he may not find a safe haven there either.</p> <p>In the worlds above, Suriel and Ozriel face off against the Mad King to determine the new shape of the cosmos. The victor will decide the fate of countless universes.</p> <p>Whether he wins or dies, Lindon will soon leave this life behind.</p> <p>The time has come to say good-bye to Cradle.</p>"; 
